The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 BTC cancels Saturdays races 

 SRIMAX

 Bangalore: A rift between the Bangalore Turf Club (BTC) authorities and trainers, pertaining to the use of mobile phones on local race days, has led to the cancellation of Saturdays programme. As a result of restrictions imposed on them, trainers have refused to accept their wards from running in Saturday races. The trainers, it is also learnt, will continue to adopt pressure tactics until the impasse is resolved.




